==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: shuĭ néng zăi zhōu, yì néng fù zhōu

===Etymology===
Literally: The water that bears the boat is the same that swallows it.

===Proverb===
'''[[水]][[能]][[載]][[舟]]，[[亦]][[能]][[覆]][[舟]]'''
# If something is used correctly, it will be of benefit.  If used incorrectly, it will do harm.
===Alternate forms===
[[水能载舟，亦能覆舟]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
